<h2 id="fulfillment-events">Fulfillment Events</h2>

<p>A Fulfillment Event represents a tracking event belonging to the orderâ€™s fulfillment. Fulfillment events are displayed on the order tracking page to give buyers visibility on their shipment status.</p>

<h3 id="get-ordersorder_idfulfillments">GET /orders/{order_id}/fulfillments</h3>

